thread.title: Patricia Wooters
thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Patricia Wooters

author: Patricia Wooters
title: Patricia Wooters
text: I always enjoy your puzzles, they are of high quality and the selection is great. One thing: Item #1086 "Ready for a Drive" had eleven duplicate pieces and one more that didn't belong at all. Not a complaint, just sort of a heads-up!!!
